high_descs: Turn around and face the sink.
Pick the glass up from the sink.
Go to the right and stand in front of the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the glass in and shut the door and then open the door and take the glass out and shut the door again.
Go left and then left again and then turn to the right to face the brown shelves.
Put the glass on the middle shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled glass on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn around to your left walk straight to the sink
Pick up the glass in front of the sink
Turn to your right and head to the fridge
Open the fridge put in and out the glass then close the fridge
Turn to your left move forward the left again head toward the shelf beside the counter
Put the glass on the edge of the second level of the shelf
anns.task_desc: Put the cold glass on the shelf

high_descs: Move to the sink to the right of the stove
Pick up a cup from the sink
Move to the fridge to the right of the sink
Chill the cup for a moment in the fridge before picking it up and closing the door
Move to the wooden shelf behind you
Place the cup on the self
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled cup on the wooden self.
